  "detailed_description": "New action game, created with Unreal Engine 5!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Climb</h2>The city is already corrupted.<br>Climb the skyscrapers of Tokyo and fend off the assassins of the Metropolitan Police Department.<br>Rescue the precious Grand Lady waiting for you at the top of the Radio Tower and dismantle the hostile corporate coalition.<br><br>■Cyberpunk city.<br>■Play through the simple game of three stages at once.<br>■The stage composition changes with each challenge.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431230/extras/6ce6e0ab1aa8a52f7868a79c8ed1e45d.poster.avif?t=1696585911\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431230/extras/6ce6e0ab1aa8a52f7868a79c8ed1e45d.webm?t=1696585911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431230/extras/6ce6e0ab1aa8a52f7868a79c8ed1e45d.mp4?t=1696585911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>■Use the physics to master the maneuvers and climb higher!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431230/extras/16541e417431a16fc07b8f72b26ada43.poster.avif?t=1696585911\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431230/extras/16541e417431a16fc07b8f72b26ada43.webm?t=1696585911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431230/extras/16541e417431a16fc07b8f72b26ada43.mp4?t=1696585911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>■Use hook shots to move and guns and swords to attack.<br>■Aerial battles with Tokyo cops.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431230/extras/5128a97aeefede79324d468ff163544b.poster.avif?t=1696585911\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431230/extras/5128a97aeefede79324d468ff163544b.webm?t=1696585911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431230/extras/5128a97aeefede79324d468ff163544b.mp4?t=1696585911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>■Never give up, no matter how many times you fall!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431230/extras/a6eb076fc1970802c64a8c2064cd49a6.poster.avif?t=1696585911\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431230/extras/a6eb076fc1970802c64a8c2064cd49a6.webm?t=1696585911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431230/extras/a6eb076fc1970802c64a8c2064cd49a6.mp4?t=1696585911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
